      "name": "Mesh convergence study — FDA pump at 3500 rpm, 5 L/min",
      "description": "Richardson extrapolation applied to three systematically refined meshes (2.1 M, 5.8 M, 14.2 M cells). Grid convergence index (GCI) for area-averaged wall shear stress < 2.3%. Hemolysis index variation across refinement levels < 1.8%. Convergence criterion satisfied.",
      "outcome": "passed"
