      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Velocity field comparison against PIV measurements",
      "description": "Simulated velocity magnitude profiles at three axial planes compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) data from Jones et al. (2019). Mean absolute error 4.1% of bulk velocity; R² = 0.94. SST k-omega turbulence model selected on basis of best agreement.",
      "outcome": "passed"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-vr-03-pressure-rise-bench",
