      "name": "Pump pressure-rise validation against bench test data",
      "description": "Predicted hydraulic pressure rise at 5 operating points compared against benchtop measurements using water analogue fluid. Mean relative error 3.7%. All predictions within ±5% of measured values, satisfying the acceptance criterion for hydraulic performance.",
      "outcome": "passed"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-vr-04-rh-index-predicate",
