      "rationale": "Pump geometry from FDA benchmark CAD file (v3, publicly released). Blood viscosity modeled as Newtonian with mu=0.0035 Pa·s (justified for high-shear CPB regime). Inlet flow rates and rotational speeds from clinical CPB operating specifications. All inputs documented with uncertainty bounds. Required level 2 achieved."
